language Essence 1.3

given v, b, r, k, lambda : int(1..)

find design : relation of (int(1..v) * int(1..b))

such that
    forAll point : int(1..v) .
        (sum block : int(1..b) . toInt((point, block) in design)) = r,
    forAll block : int(1..b) .
        (sum point : int(1..v) . toInt((point, block) in design)) = k,
    forAll p1 : int(1..v) . forAll p2 : int(p1+1..v) .
        (sum block : int(1..b) . toInt((p1, block) in design /\ (p2, block) in design)) = lambda
